item.description: I’m in my first year towards a master’s degree in Bioinformatics at the LMU and Technical University of Munich. After finishing my bachelor’s thesis on breast cancer radiomics, I continued to work at the Chair of Experimental Bioinformatics in Weihenstephan as a student research assistant to further develop my thesis project.
